1
00:01:54,959 --> 00:01:57,000
Yang Yunfan, you're finally here.

2
00:01:57,719 --> 00:01:59,840
Who are you? What are you doing here?

3
00:02:01,239 --> 00:02:03,519
You actually don't remember me?

4
00:02:03,519 --> 00:02:06,760
Do you know how hard it's been waiting for you?

5
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:10,599
You little brat.

6
00:02:10,599 --> 00:02:11,759
How do you know about me?

7
00:02:12,199 --> 00:02:14,280
Tell me, who are you really?

8
00:02:14,479 --> 00:02:15,719
You've changed so much.

9
00:02:15,719 --> 00:02:17,080
But I still recognized you.

10
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:17,840
It's me!

11
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:19,639
The Realm Spirit of the Heart-Questioning Realm.

12
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,599
Yunfan!

13
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:36,919
Don't run away!

14
00:02:36,919 --> 00:02:38,240
Let's go play together!

15
00:02:39,639 --> 00:02:40,960
Stop! Don't run!

16
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:41,759
Time to play!

17
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:50,080
You little brat, got you now!

18
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,560
A ruffled hen turned into a demon!

19
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,919
It's a demon!

20
00:02:55,439 --> 00:02:56,759
Wha-

21
00:02:56,759 --> 00:02:57,719
What old hen?

22
00:02:59,599 --> 00:03:01,120
If anything, I'm a big rooster!

23
00:03:01,639 --> 00:03:03,439
You little brat, tell Master.

24
00:03:03,439 --> 00:03:05,159
Did you stick that on Master?

25
00:03:06,639 --> 00:03:08,199
It definitely wasn't me!

26
00:03:08,199 --> 00:03:09,960
With my tiny arms and legs,

27
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:11,759
how could I catch a chicken?

28
00:03:11,759 --> 00:03:14,599
That's a full-grown hen.

29
00:03:14,599 --> 00:03:16,120
I'm not even grown up yet!

30
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:17,879
Oh, you're not grown up yet?

31
00:03:17,879 --> 00:03:19,960
All day you pull these crooked tricks.

32
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,560
See how Master deals with you.

33
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:24,439
I'll teach you a lesson!

34
00:03:24,439 --> 00:03:26,039
Still running?

35
00:03:26,039 --> 00:03:26,479
Running again?

36
00:03:30,439 --> 00:03:31,879
You little brat!

37
00:03:32,319 --> 00:03:33,919
Master knows you miss your dad.

38
00:03:35,159 --> 00:03:38,159
You've been doing well with the Primordial Violet Qi Art lately.

39
00:03:38,159 --> 00:03:40,800
Master grants you leave to visit your dad.

40
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:41,840
How's that sound?

41
00:03:42,639 --> 00:03:45,000
Really, Master? I can go down the mountain?

42
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:45,960
Of course.

43
00:03:47,439 --> 00:03:49,680
You're finally wising up.

44
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,240
Acting all grown up, are you?

45
00:03:53,319 --> 00:03:55,400
"Finally wising up," he says!

46
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,680
Listen here, you little brat.

47
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:58,439
If you act up again,

48
00:03:58,439 --> 00:04:00,080
I'll go find Little Qingxue,

49
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:01,719
and tell her not to play with you.

50
00:04:01,719 --> 00:04:05,800
She won't play with you anymore!

51
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:13,360
Dad! Mom!

52
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:13,840
Little Fan

53
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,800
I'm back

54
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:15,840
You're home

55
00:04:17,199 --> 00:04:18,519
Let Mom take a look at you

56
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,720
How did you get so thin?

57
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:22,040
Couldn't get used to the food on the mountain?

58
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:23,240
Was it really tough?

59
00:04:24,199 --> 00:04:25,000
Wait a moment

60
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:27,519
I'll go make your favorite braised pork

61
00:04:27,519 --> 00:04:28,439
I'll tell the kitchen right away

62
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:29,560
Never mind

63
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,480
I'd better go do it myself

64
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,199
Wait for Mom

65
00:04:34,519 --> 00:04:36,160
Come, let me see if you've lost weight

66
00:04:36,160 --> 00:04:37,319
Not at all

67
00:04:39,839 --> 00:04:42,240
You're clearly still a little chubby!

68
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,439
Let me hold you

69
00:04:45,879 --> 00:04:47,040
You're pretty heavy

70
00:04:48,839 --> 00:04:49,759
Little troublemaker

71
00:04:49,759 --> 00:04:50,800
I heard

72
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:52,920
someone threw a chicken into the Medicine Sovereign's bed

73
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:53,800
Was that you?

74
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:54,720
No, no

75
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:55,600
It was you

76
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:57,720
Still lying!

77
00:04:58,519 --> 00:04:59,240
Let me tell you

78
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,639
If you're really that bold

79
00:05:00,639 --> 00:05:02,439
let's overthrow your dad right now

80
00:05:02,439 --> 00:05:04,079
How about you become my boss?

81
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:07,240
Let me see who's plotting against me

82
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:08,240
Master, it was him

83
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,240
Was it you?

84
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,399
You want to be my boss?

85
00:05:14,839 --> 00:05:15,600
Her

86
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,639
Come here

87
00:05:16,639 --> 00:05:17,720
Give me a hug

88
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:18,240
Let me see

89
00:05:20,959 --> 00:05:22,279
Did Song Ci teach you this?

90
00:05:23,759 --> 00:05:24,680
No!

91
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:25,639
It has nothing to do with me

92
00:05:26,319 --> 00:05:28,480
Your master complained to me

93
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:30,519
He said you've become really naughty

94
00:05:30,519 --> 00:05:32,319
Daring to stuff a chicken in his bed

95
00:05:33,319 --> 00:05:34,199
Is that right?

96
00:05:34,199 --> 00:05:34,759
Did you do it?

97
00:05:36,519 --> 00:05:37,680
If not you, then who?

98
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:39,879
It was her

99
00:05:39,879 --> 00:05:41,000
She taught me

100
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:41,920
Let me take a good look

101
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:50,399
What's wrong?

102
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,759
Mom, wake up!

103
00:05:53,759 --> 00:05:55,519
Wake up!

104
00:05:55,519 --> 00:05:56,839
Please wake up!

105
00:05:58,399 --> 00:05:59,519
What's happening to you?

106
00:05:59,519 --> 00:06:00,240
What's wrong?

107
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,560
Please wake up!

108
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:42,879
Master.

109
00:06:49,519 --> 00:06:50,959
The Mystic Medicine Association

110
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,759
has a traitor.

111
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:01,279
I'll make them pay.

112
00:07:03,639 --> 00:07:05,360
Yunfan, listen to me.

113
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:08,680
In the cave on the back mountain,

114
00:07:10,639 --> 00:07:12,360
there lies the Medicine Heir Token

115
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:15,319
and the Medicine Venerable Token.

116
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:20,319
From now on, you're the Medicine Prodigy of the Mystic Medicine Association.

117
00:07:23,079 --> 00:07:24,439
You bear

118
00:07:25,839 --> 00:07:27,839
the Primordial Violet Qi Art.

119
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:31,480
You're the only hope for me and your father.

120
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,120
I don't want it.

121
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,639
I don't want any of it.

122
00:07:35,639 --> 00:07:37,000
I just want you to live, Master.

123
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:42,839
Never let hatred

124
00:07:42,839 --> 00:07:45,040
blind you.

125
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:48,040
I don't want this.

126
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,399
Master!

127
00:07:49,399 --> 00:07:50,920
I'll avenge you.

128
00:07:51,839 --> 00:07:53,920
When the Primordial Violet Qi flows in reverse,

129
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:56,600
one falls into demonic corruption.

130
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:12,360
Once you've mastered it,

131
00:08:14,519 --> 00:08:16,959
then come and hate me.

132
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:39,399
Medicine Sovereign Fuguang is incredibly powerful.

133
00:08:39,399 --> 00:08:42,440
He hid all your memories inside me.

134
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:45,679
Now you've finally got them all back.

135
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:56,039
Master.

136
00:08:56,039 --> 00:08:58,799
You've now mastered the Primordial Violet Qi Art.

137
00:08:58,799 --> 00:09:00,840
You're the greatest in the world right now.

138
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:02,000
Truly formidable.

139
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:02,840
Hurry, give it a try.

140
00:09:18,639 --> 00:09:21,200
So can I pass the Heart-Questioning Realm now?

141
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,960
You've passed.

142
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:25,320
You passed it ten years ago.

143
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:26,720
That's right.

144
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:27,799
I passed it ten years ago.

145
00:09:29,799 --> 00:09:31,120
I can't waste any more time.

146
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:31,960
I have to get out of here.

147
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:35,720
I remember who you are now.

148
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,759
I'll come play with you again later.

149
00:09:43,519 --> 00:09:46,240
A thousand-mile road ends at this gate.

150
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:47,799
I was right.

151
00:09:47,799 --> 00:09:49,639
You really did pass the Heart-Questioning Realm.

152
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:58,559
Medicine Master Li, how enthusiastic of you.

153
00:09:58,559 --> 00:09:59,960
Quite the welcome you've prepared for me.

154
00:10:01,639 --> 00:10:03,600
Hand over the Primordial Violet Qi Art.

155
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:04,799
And I'll spare your life.

156
00:10:08,399 --> 00:10:09,840
The dignified Medicine Master of the Mystic Medicine Association,

157
00:10:10,759 --> 00:10:12,960
your medicine doesn't heal, but your blade sure cuts close.

158
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:14,399
Four parts ravenous ambition,

159
00:10:14,399 --> 00:10:16,039
two parts foreign espionage,

160
00:10:16,039 --> 00:10:17,200
one dose of the sect's rotten blood,

161
00:10:17,799 --> 00:10:18,759
applied externally as assassins,

162
00:10:18,759 --> 00:10:20,080
taken internally as treachery.

163
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:20,840
Li Mouren,

164
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:22,919
your formula is truly venomous.

165
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:25,720
Cut the nonsense.

166
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:27,080
Are you handing it over or not?

167
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:28,960
You want it?

168
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:32,519
Then come and take it yourself.

169
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:40,960
Move.

170
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:45,440
Behave yourself.

171
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:48,080
Yunfan!

172
00:10:54,159 --> 00:10:54,759
What?

173
00:10:55,679 --> 00:10:56,240
Won't hand it over?

174
00:10:57,399 --> 00:10:58,879
Want to watch them

175
00:10:58,879 --> 00:11:00,840
die one by one in front of you?

176
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:01,559
Don't stop.

177
00:11:03,519 --> 00:11:05,279
We'll die anyway, even if you give it up.

178
00:11:05,279 --> 00:11:06,759
Don't worry about us, Yunfan!

179
00:11:22,399 --> 00:11:23,639
Yang Yunfan.

180
00:11:24,279 --> 00:11:25,879
I gave you a chance.

181
00:11:27,039 --> 00:11:29,039
Since you didn't take it,

182
00:11:29,039 --> 00:11:30,519
now you'll pay the price.

183
00:11:35,519 --> 00:11:35,919
No!

184
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:41,639
I'll hand it over!

185
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:04,120
It wasn't me

186
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:05,240
You're the killer

187
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:05,720
No

188
00:12:05,720 --> 00:12:06,159
It's you

189
00:12:06,159 --> 00:12:06,919
Stay back, all of you!

190
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:07,840
You're the killer

191
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:08,519
No

192
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,240
It's you

193
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:20,559
Xiang'er
